{"serial": "13020", "department_serial": 12, "code": "FR2044", "class": "A", "name": {"en": "Grammar II", "ch": "文法(二)"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Lin, Te-Yu"], "ch": ["林德祐"]}, "credits": 2, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 1, "session": ["7", "8"]}, "loc": {"building": "A", "room": "226"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": true, "MaxStu": 50, "department": {"ch": "法國語文學系", "en": "Department of French"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 23, "selected": 0, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "依據一年級文法課所學，做更有系統、更深入的講解，幫助同學建立精確的文法觀，俾利口語和書寫的表達實踐。", "en": "please refer to the Chinese version"}, "outline": {"ch": "文法（二）將依據一年級文法課所學，做更有系統、更深入的講解，幫助同學建立精確文法觀。透過講解與練習，使同學能熟悉文法規則，並活用於書寫、口說與翻譯中。本課程首先針對所進行的單元作一概念介紹，講解細部規則，輔以例句。另外本課程亦針對幾個易混淆的文法規則，詳加比較，細說原理，隨即引導學生舉一反三，依規則做例句撰寫。上學期擬訂之單元: le discours indirect, le subjonctif , les pronoms relatives, les temps du passé. 下學期擬訂之單元︰ les propositions surbordonnées de cause, de conséquence, de but, de temps, d‘opposition, d‘hypothèse.", "en": "please refer to the Chinese version"}, "textbook": {"ch": "1. Dominique Jennepin, Yvonne Delatour, Brigitte Teyssier, Maylis Léon-Dufour, Nouvelle Grammaire du Français, Paris, Hachette, 2004. \n2. 350 exercices , Hachette. (niveaux moyen, superieur I et II) \n3. 450 nouveaux exercices , CLE international, niveaux debutant et moyen. \n4. 楊淑娟、Julien Chameroy《法語凱旋門: 文法圖表精解》，台北，聯經，2014年。\n5. 楊淑娟、侯義如，《法文文法瑰寶：自主學習進階版》，台北，聯經，2021年。", "en": "please refer to the Chinese version"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "40", "en": "40"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授", "en": ["Lecture"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "平時成績佔總成績30％，期中考及期末考各佔35％。", "en": "please refer to the Chinese version"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "星期一13:00-15:00   星期五15:00-17:00", "en": "please refer to the Chinese version"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "